<div class="layout">
<a href="/">百度百科</a>&nbsp;>&nbsp;寒露&nbsp;>&nbsp;历史版本
</div>
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-versionInfoCard">
<div class="versionInfoCard-content">
这是本词条的历史版本，由<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uname=_%E5%90%9B%E5%AD%90%E5%A6%82%E5%85%B0&from=lemma" target="_blank">_君子如兰</a>于2018-11-11 10:51:07
贡献。<div class="jump-area">
<a href="/history/%E5%AF%92%E9%9C%B2/489013/133409478?fromAction=prev" class="cmn-btn cmn-btn-32">上一版本</a><a href="/history/%E5%AF%92%E9%9C%B2/489013/134818952?fromAction=next" class="cmn-btn cmn-btn-32">下一版本</a><a href="/history/%E5%AF%92%E9%9C%B2/489013/140721302?fromAction=latest" class="cmn-btn cmn-btn-32">最新版本</a></div>
